# uv / pip
# NOTE: .python-version is INTENTIONALLY tracked. Render's uv-managed
# build sandbox needs it to know which Python interpreter to install
# (uv 0.10.2's `python-downloads=never` default will not auto-fetch a
# Python 3.12 interpreter on its own).